des:
Deep Rest is the Alexa skill that offers guided sessions to help you achieve ultimate relaxation and drift into a state of deep, restorative rest. With over 10 unique sessions, each lasting 10 minutes, and a variety of soothing voices paired with calming background sounds, this skill is crafted to ease your body and mind into a peaceful state.

⭐ PREMIUM FEATURES ⭐

• Guided sessions with professional, soothing voices
• A selection of background sounds tailored for deep rest and relaxation
• Unlimited access with no restrictions
• Regularly updated programs to refine your relaxation journey
• Full access to all session lengths

We value your feedback to help us enhance your experience and provide the ultimate solution for relaxation and rest.

Begin your journey to a state of true Deep Rest!
